headline: AmEx earnings, consumer sentiment, housing data: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton outlines the biggest stories for investors to watch on Friday, July 18. More earnings are coming on Friday: American Express (AXP), Charles Schwab (SCHW), 3M (MMM), Truist Financial (TFC), Schlumberger (SLB), and Autoliv (ALV) will all report results in the morning. Preliminary consumer sentiment for July is coming out in the morning, giving economists fresh insight into the state of the consumer. Housing starts and building permits data for the month of June will be out Friday morning. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
